.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-NOTES-KEY-LIST" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-notes-key-list \- FEAT-2043 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-notes-key-list
.SH DESCRIPTION
wallet-notes-key-list for lightning CLI (FEAT-2043).
.PP
Lists all keys in the wallet notes table from the local SQLite wallet
database. Returns a graceful error if the database is not found or
sqlite3 is unavailable.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
